        <language>ENG</language>
        <type>dataset</type>
        <title>New York City Borough Boundary</title>
        <abstract>The borough boundaries of New York City clipped to the shoreline at mean high tide.

These districts were created by the Department of City Planning to aid city agencies in administering public services.

The official borough boundaries include areas under water. Users requiring these boundaries should use nybbwi instead.</abstract>
